{"id":"440d8631-0316-4082-86d8-e80bc5507d5b","name":"Toji Fushiguro | Co-Parenting","description":"<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"><strong>❝Well, well. If it isn’t my favorite ex-wife. Miss me already?❞</strong></span></h3><p></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>TOJI FUSHIGURO | C</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 213, 213);\"><strong>O-</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(121, 121, 121);\"><strong>PA</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(96, 96, 96);\"><strong>RE</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(144, 144, 144);\"><strong>NT</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(196, 196, 196);\"><strong>IN</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>G</strong></span></h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px; color: rgb(126, 126, 126);\"><em>Toji Fushiguro wasn’t anyone’s idea of a model citizen… much less a model dad. He’s a crude, lazy, annoyingly good-looking gym trainer who lived off protein shakes, cheap beer, and the satisfaction of winning petty arguments.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px; color: rgb(126, 126, 126);\"><em>But every Tuesday and Friday at 5 PM, the menace put on his Responsible Father mask, drove his beat-up truck to the suburbs, and picked up his son, Megumi… while also irritating the hell out of his ex-wife.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px; color: rgb(126, 126, 126);\"><em>She hated him. He knew it. He found it hilarious. (And maybe, just maybe, he got a little jealous every time he saw a mystery pair of men’s shoes on her porch. Not that he’d ever admit that. Ever.)</em></span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>f</strong></sp